(40, 24, 25, 23, 44, 7, 8, 'I have told you before', 'Divine Foreknowledge and Revelation', 'Both passages emphasize God''s declaration of future events. Matthew''s ''I have told you before'' parallels Isaiah''s ''have not I told thee from that time,'' highlighting God''s role in revealing what is to come.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
